{subhead}*22.4.2000 Shortcuts to our product-pages*{def}
{left}
{p} {p}
Up to today, our product-pages were only reachable via several clicks.{p}
From today on these are reachable via subdomain-shortcuts and directly show the requested product-page:{p}
        http://fxpaint.innovative-web.de/{p}
        http://fxscan.innovative-web.de/{p}
        http://mlcpro.innovative-web.de/{p}
        http://ultraconv.innovative-web.de/{p}
        http://vhistudio.innovative-web.de/
{p} {p}
The page of the VHI-standard also has a new address:{p}
        http://vhi.innovative-web.de/
{p} {p}
If you like our products, we would be thankful for a link from your homepage.
{p} {p}
*22.4.2000 Pictures = Files .. the new Stargate-Plugin for fxPAINT*{p}
The latest version of the stargate-plugin allows you to access pictures
loaded into fxPAINT as files. Furthermore it is possible to send images directly to
fxPAINT. PhotoAlbum, CyberShow, Superview, VHI Studio NG and Ultraconv NG already support the
"Stargate Airport".
